Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:06.90,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In this kingdom where magic is everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:11.02,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,there is one boy who can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:11.97,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:16.62,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He puts in blood, sweat, and tears \Nin hopes of becoming the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:22.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But there are also those in the kingdom \Nwho possess at least a little bit of mana,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:26.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,yet can barely use any magic at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:32.38,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The very few out of the population, \Nthose who live in the shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:40.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They are also trying to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:56.57,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I? What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:58.65,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:00.25,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.76,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,You're... one of Asta and \NBig Brother's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:05.73,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:09.63,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Though I wish we could escape, \Nour mana has been sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:14.91,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,The magic item I borrowed from Asta to let \Npeople know of our location is gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:19.38,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we? Who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:22.91,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing we have in common is that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:26.12,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,we were suspected of being servants \Nof the devil at the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:29.56,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably trying to take \Nadvantage of that somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:33.57,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,This is all for the sake of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:36.06,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Master Kabwe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:40.53,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,We must rid this world of the devil's \Nservants who brought destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:43.08,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,and chaos to this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:46.50,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:13.25,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\move(315,95,315,90)\t(1,4650,\fs24)\fad(1000,1)}Rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.51,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(731,1)\blur3}The City of Lehart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:25.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.94,main,No mask C,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil Banishers are the bringers \Nof justice we've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.76,main,No mask C,0000,0000,0000,,Bring death to servants of the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.38,main,Group,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:35.64,main,No mask G,0000,0000,0000,,Let there be blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.20,main,Noble woman,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.83,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:50.28,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they do that to \Nmy angel?! I'll kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.10,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. Looks like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.38,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nero, Marie, we're here to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:03.00,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a message from Julius, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.85,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like all the squads are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:08.39,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost noon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:11.35,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,when the Devil Banishers said \Nthey'd execute them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.73,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know how many \Nenemies we're dealing with,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:17.36,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,and we expect them to use \Nvarious drugs as well as magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.25,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This will probably prove difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:23.61,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like you to do everything \Nyou can to save the captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:27.22,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,First, the Silver Eagles \Nand the Crimson Lion Kings
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:31.50,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,will help with the rescue and protect \Nthe civilians who have gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:36.38,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue Rose Knights and the Green \NPraying Mantises will patrol the square.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:42.55,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And the core squad that will save the \Nhostages will be the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You got it. By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:48.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,there seems to be someone here who \Nhas nothing to do with the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He may be here because he feels some guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:54.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,considering his subordinates are behind this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.65,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but we can't just have him acting on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.15,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The rescue is our primary objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:05.57,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Are you willing to go along with our plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.32,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,That was my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.16,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd like to confirm something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.78,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,If Asta uses the powers of the \Ndevil in front of the masses,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:16.80,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,he will only bring more confusion and chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.02,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,I ask that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:20.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He not use it for this plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, dumbasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:27.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone other than the kid and Gauche, \Nkeep an eye on the square like we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:30.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The lives of two of our own are \Nat stake. Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.81,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.83,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:38.41,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,As you requested, we are having the other \Nsquads keep an eye on the Noble Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.98,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we must consider that\N the execution could be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:44.14,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,a ruse to distract us while \Nthey wreak havoc elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:48.29,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,We must make sure this plan is \Na success, to ensure this incident
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:51.37,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't cause greater panic \Namong the masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.73,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Let's have faith in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:06:01.59,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,So far, we haven't seen anything unusual. \NI hope they're able to rescue them safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:04.75,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Since Captain Vangeance is away \Nkeeping an eye on the border,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:07.33,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,we aren't able to assist in \Nthe main part of this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.89,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But be alert for even the smallest detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.00,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.35,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, why are we on patrol duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:15.96,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be able to beat up any enemy in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just here to complete my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.42,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.65,main,No mask C,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time! The purveyors \Nof justice will soon arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.86,main,No mask G,0000,0000,0000,,We can't count on the Magic Parliament\N or the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:36.15,main,No mask G,0000,0000,0000,,Our true saviors are the Devil Banishers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.26,main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.29,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let justice be served!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.42,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are probably \Nsomewhere in this crowd, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:44.00,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to find them, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.80,italics,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they've all lost their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.88,italics,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Did they use some kind \Nof weird drug on them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.13,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Tch. I can't just sit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:05.17,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami, let me go down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna ruin the plan \Nif you go down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:14.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't just sit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're the cornerstone of this plan, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So just sit and wait your damn turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:20.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:23.96,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,There's still no sign of them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.71,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:40.06,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, I don't see anyone suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.34,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.76,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.22,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.36,main,No mask C,0000,0000,0000,,Witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:50.65,main,No mask G,0000,0000,0000,,If you want your friends to live, \Nyou will do as we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:56.41,main,No mask G,0000,0000,0000,,Do anything rash, and we will kill your \Nfriends before the public execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:59.54,main,No mask C,0000,0000,0000,,Walk toward the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:04.19,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this was mentioned, \Nbut I really didn't sense their mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:09.16,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. I'm sure the others \Nwill be able to save Nero and Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.40,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.92,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,To all who despise the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:26.69,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,The time to strike in the \Nname of justice as arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:31.10,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Devil Banishers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.73,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,We are the ones who wish for the devil's demise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.90,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.30,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Calm your asses down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:48.34,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,So it does appear that they can prevent \Ntheir mana from being detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.09,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the only ones using \Nthe items are those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.31,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Behold this woman's horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:03.18,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,This is solid proof that she sold her soul \Nto the devil and used forbidden magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.69,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How mortifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.90,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's the devil herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:10.50,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,The little girl next to her became a servant \Nof the devil along with her brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.90,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,who is a former criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:16.52,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,We know it's the undeniable truth \Nthat they have harmed many!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.63,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that innocent, harmless expression!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.05,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just execute them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.16,top,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Let us have our justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.66,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,She should've been executed before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:25.78,main,Mage A,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lord Damnatio, if that \Nbarrier spell explodes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.67,main,Mage A,0000,0000,0000,,many civilians will be harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:35.30,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Kabwe... Does your justice involve \Nrisking the lives of innocent people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:40.55,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,That spell is probably the work \Nof Mole Chin Scales' subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:42.62,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,But we mustn't forget that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:47.39,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,there is one possessed by the devil whom\Nwe must hate even more than these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.99,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.65,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:59.16,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, our greatest desire \Nis to see you executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.95,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,You are the true cause of this chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:04.95,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,We know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.37,top,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:07.96,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like Mister Yami said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.96,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him in the papers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.17,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That peasant is here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:11.46,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Like they'd stop any of this \Nif Asta did come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:15.57,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,If you show yourself and \Nallow us to detain you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.72,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,we will let these two go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nero! Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.98,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:36.25,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Is your life more precious \Nthan your friends' after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.62,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.49,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You evil servant of the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:42.43,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Asta would \Nabandon his friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:46.58,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. If you refuse to show yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.25,main,G Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.13,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:07.81,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see Vanessa, but we don't \Nhave time to find her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.50,main,No mask H,0000,0000,0000,,You accursed devil-possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:13.12,main,No mask H,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, he's the one who \Nmessed up this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.16,main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you ruin my family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.36,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.91,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Execute him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:20.63,main,G asta,0000,0000,0000,,We don't serve the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.08,main,No mask H,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.79,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:35.38,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Give them your grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.67,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Did that ruin your plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:44.82,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,We know that you hope to undo \Nthe barrier with your anti-magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.90,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:47.61,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and give it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:50.39,main,G asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna free Nero and Marie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:53.13,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We already established that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:56.61,main,G asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then put down your swords \Nand step away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.74,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:03.45,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give us your grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:04.84,main,G asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.64,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:09.70,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.20,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,another Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:15.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting for you to \Nlook away from the hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:23.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Dark Cloaked Lightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.26,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:35.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping potion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:37.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not gonna work anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.03,main,Siona,0000,0000,0000,,Paper Magic: Dagger-Folding \NEarly Summer Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nero! Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:49.06,main,Siona,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:55.83,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.62,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.06,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:06.98,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.68,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.40,main,Masses,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.68,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Our comrades will buy us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.73,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Transparency Magic: Share the Same Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nero! Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way. Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, where are ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Magic: Sea Dragon's Lair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? My magic control is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.85,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,It's closing in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.96,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Finral! Where's Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.68,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta went after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.56,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to chase after them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:05.09,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,but this smoke is affecting \Nmy sight, and my magic is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:08.15,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,The trap spells I set up throughout \Nthe square aren't responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:12.16,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there's something in \Nthis smoke that disrupts mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.57,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Those dirty little...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:22.92,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Mister Yami! \NThe smoke's no match for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:31.68,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Go help evacuate the masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:36.22,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,On your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.44,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:59.62,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.48,main,No mask C,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:06.38,main,No mask G,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission was to get you away from \Nthe square since you have magic
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:10.01,main,No mask G,0000,0000,0000,,that can change fate in your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:14.26,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I see... But even without changing fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.64,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I know my friends have rescued the hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.66,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have to listen to you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:24.29,main,No mask C,0000,0000,0000,,We know we can't defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:27.59,main,No mask C,0000,0000,0000,,We also know they'll read our \Nmemories if we're captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.64,main,No mask G,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:34.39,main,No mask G,0000,0000,0000,,We're willing to risk our lives for this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:51.32,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No... They just took their own lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:55.68,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This plan is that important to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:59.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel their ki over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:03.99,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:10.03,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,You followed us without realizing \Nthat we wanted you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:14.06,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Put your grimoire here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:17.24,main,some,0000,0000,0000,,If you resist, these girls will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.24,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:22.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:27.58,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,What could you possibly do \Nwithout the powers of the devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:46.32,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Master Kabwe, let's take \Nthem before the others arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:48.71,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,No, we'll take care of them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.19,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that's not according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:55.20,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights are far more \Npowerful than I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:59.17,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,We were lucky everything went well so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:02.72,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,but if we want to succeed, \Nour only chance is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.07,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.71,main,Mask E,0000,0000,0000,,You coward! Why are you so scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.51,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.06,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for your insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.60,main,Mask D,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.06,main,Siona,0000,0000,0000,,You accursed devil-possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:28.94,main,Siona,0000,0000,0000,,If you dodge, these will hit the little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.57,main,Siona,0000,0000,0000,,Paper Magic: Dagger-Folding \NEarly Summer Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:40.62,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:45.50,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,So you must be the Devil Banishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:48.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno?! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:52.45,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,We just happened to be patrolling \Nthe area and wandered by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.64,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Pure coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:18:00.33,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This is slightly outside of our mission, \Nbut Captain Vangeance did say to patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:02.71,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:05.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But more importantly, \Ntake care of Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.94,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:18.37,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,We almost got our hands on Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:21.22,main,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get caught here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Give Nero back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:33.09,main,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Come any closer and the girl dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:36.75,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, wait. You're running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:38.19,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:48.51,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,A devil resides in the \Nfive-leaf-clover grimoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:50.60,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.54,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:00.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.49,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:01.91,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa, check on Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:05.98,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:11.18,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,They stole his grimoire... \NHow vile could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:16.58,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You still have magic you can use even \Nif they take your grimoire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.72,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.88,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:24.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:42.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get Nero and my grimoire back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.21,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.93,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:02.51,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon for you to become a real angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:06.51,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:11.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,According to Owen, she'll need a \Nlittle more time before she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.17,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,So Marie's okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:15.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:17.48,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.78,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I owe you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:30.09,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Today, it became clear that my subordinates \Nare involved in this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:33.25,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,First, let me apologize for \Nmy lack of supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.15,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You said they had a strong sense of justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:40.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but they took the crowd hostage. \NThat's nothing more than playing dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:44.94,main,Vengeance,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he's being fooled and \Nmanipulated by the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:50.77,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Stealing Asta's grimoire could \Nbe someone else's intent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:55.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're here at this meeting now, \Nbut you weren't here earlier, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:21:00.18,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,After you cried and swore your \Nloyalty to the boss, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:05.41,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yami. I'm the one who \Nasked him to watch the borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:09.35,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The worst thing that could happen right now \Nis for the Spade Kingdom to make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:12.80,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:18.92,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Looking through the memories of \Nthe Devil Banishers we captured
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:22.11,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,tells us that most of them were paid hires.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:26.78,main,Mage A,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for interrupting, \Nbut this is urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.33,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:30.56,main,Mage A,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, we received a message from Kabwe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:31.95,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:35.94,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Kabwe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.44,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:47.89,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,They... aren't after the demise of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:54.45,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,They're actually... trying to \Ngain the powers of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:56.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:22:01.29,italics,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,They are those who worship the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:04.38,italics,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil Believers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:42.71,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're \Nall right, my angel Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.71,0:23:44.90,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:48.90,main,Some,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 146:\N "Those Who Worship the Devil."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 146\N\N{\fs18} Those Who Worship the Devil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:52.68,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be satisfied until \NI beat the crap out of them!
